<head>ATHEISM</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">無神主義</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>DENIAL that DEITIES EXIT.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>無神主義 refers to the ideology of atheism.</p>
<p>無神論 refers to the dogma of atheism.</p>
<p>rough draft to BEGIN TO identify synonym group members for analysis, based on CL etc. 18.11.2003. CH ／</p>
